Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能杀了他们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 奈落大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 弥勒 还有珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 奈落大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被窃取的铁碎牙 决战 奈落之城！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我让他忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀所有的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把犬夜叉的刀铁碎牙抢来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就让琥珀永远活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…刚刚睡醒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会杀了他…虽然觉得很对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了 那个人根本不是琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是琥珀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我弟弟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不可能做出杀死村民的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要…把他跟奈落一起除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么简单吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的容貌没有任何变化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真能轻易的憎恨他 忘了他的一切吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能落入这种卑劣的圈套里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换做是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能也下不了手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为容貌丝毫没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是无法憎恨或遗忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉说的是桔梗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大意 我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 弥勒！你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的风穴还没完全康复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别为了那些杂碎去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只要由我来干掉头目就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂碎给我滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度的力量也想跟我交手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！可恶可恶 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太心软了 实在太心软了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奈落的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非杀了这小子不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这种人 死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 伙伴 还有村人们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 像我这种人…死了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…你干什么？你想怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子想把四魂碎片取出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才弄伤自己的背部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维系着琥珀性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是埋在他体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把它取出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀立刻就会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在试探我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看我能不能亲手送上铁碎牙吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的本意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？犬夜叉 还有弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没消失 那小鬼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的血腥味还残留着 一直闻的到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落在引诱我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴被封印 铁碎牙又被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他的 我还有这双拳头！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先将飞来骨放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遵照约定把犬夜叉的刀 铁碎牙带来了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我见琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我才会把刀给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 现在马上把琥珀变回原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使把我杀了也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能不清楚这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是四魂之玉造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要四魂碎片的妖怪 袭击了你的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲的死 琥珀徘徊在生与死之间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是四魂之玉的因果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你杀害了父亲与伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为你想要四魂之玉的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就被你杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人因四魂之力而生 亦因四魂之力而死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要厌恶四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀就是依靠它的力量生存着的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依照约定 是用刀换琥珀吧 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙无耻 什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的答案 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城的少主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荫刀是个宅心仁厚的主君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他慎重地埋葬了除妖师的骸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派人去保护你的 也是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了他吗 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人见荫刀…现在我就是城主 荫刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比我的瘴气更毒的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 愿意跟琥珀一起在这城中侍奉我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荫刀也说过呢 叫你回到城中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少给我胡说八道 除掉你才是我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了父亲和伙伴的仇恨 我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到城了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是奈落的城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是珊瑚的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 快醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那双手杀了弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后只需渴望 渴望自己能生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想让自己得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了琥珀 染上鲜血之时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片就能增加黑暗之光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之光正因为其污浊 才更美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵…怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能下得了手杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…下不了手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被弟弟所伤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了…为何做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落…你在哪 滚出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害父亲与同伴的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐却无法取其性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟比她自己的生命更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何能达到如此境界 我实在想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一点 只差一点就能恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 这不是跟你当年的情况一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟50年前的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让珊瑚憎恨弟弟 让她亲手杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此 他背上的四魂碎片就会沾染邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和让彼此信赖的桔梗与犬夜叉互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自相残杀的圈套一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕 我绝对无法饶恕这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像桔梗为了不让四魂之玉被污染而死去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚也…没有与弟弟交战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那家伙真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚怎么可能会做出那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为珊瑚…是个爱护弟弟的好姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是瘴气！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肤浅的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淹没在瘴气之海中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过父亲说了哦 琥珀的功夫越来越好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次被父亲夸奖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你还不能乱动…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你别乱动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会我还有一大堆怨言跟你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了！奈落…那家伙拥有四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落！觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落…你真是太差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人…这种力量是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将邪念 瘴气和毒气都一扫而空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种力量是桔梗的…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你求饶我也不会原谅你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这的确就是桔梗的破魔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这丫头是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 它穿透瘴气把奈落射穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不能放开云母哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那是城的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落逃走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…因为四魂碎片消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我没能干掉奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用自责 若没有戈薇小姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大家早就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 好像刚才的你是目前为止最强的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…绝对要打倒奈落哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多么艰难 大家都要同心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 珊瑚 不能乱动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点阻止她 珊瑚好像想走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底 你想去什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我已无法跟大家在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 大家都知道你是因为弟弟才被奈落欺骗的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会再背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要琥珀还在奈落手里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你打算一个人去讨伐奈落吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以…让大家一起去救你的弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落不是你一个人能对付的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 首先得包扎伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你唧唧歪歪的吵死了 大家在一起就是比较好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你也蛮会打架的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连轻易被夺走铁碎牙的犬夜叉都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？应该没有问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说的好像是我很呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说你心胸宽大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚讨厌我们大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的缘故 使大家遭受这种危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后可能还会重蹈覆辙…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…一直都很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不要紧了 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有大家陪着你
